## Your Task

Implement method resolution in `src/type_checker.zig` and `src/interpreter.zig` — when a method call like `x.eq(y)` is encountered, look up the impl block for the type of `x` and dispatch to the correct method. (per DESIGN.md section "Standard Library") Tests should cover: calling trait method on concrete type, calling method on type with no impl produces error, method resolution with multiple impls for different types.

